sequenceDiagram
    participant Endpoint as Endpoint / Server
    participant Agent as Wazuh Agent
    participant Manager as Wazuh Manager
    participant VT as VirusTotal
    participant Dashboard as Wazuh Dashboard
    participant Slack as Slack Channel
    participant Analyst as Security Analyst

    Endpoint->>Agent: Security event, file change, Defender alert, login failure
    Agent->>Manager: Forward normalised event
    Manager->>Manager: Decode, correlate, apply rules
    Manager->>VT: Optional hash or indicator reputation lookup
    VT-->>Manager: Reputation result
    Manager->>Dashboard: Store and display alert
    Manager->>Slack: Send high-value notification
    Slack->>Analyst: Analyst receives alert and triages
